      <title>数据结构第一次单元测试</title>
      <link href="/posts/15542.html"/>
      <url>/posts/15542.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="补充知识"><a href="#补充知识" class="headerlink" title="补充知识"></a>补充知识</h3><h4 id="pass"><a href="#pass" class="headerlink" title="pass"></a>pass</h4><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>R1-2</strong> 所谓“循环队列”是指用单向循环链表或者循环数组表示的队列。**<font color=red> F </font>**</p><p><strong>【解】</strong> 循环队列是一个抽象的数据结构，而单向循环链表和循环数组都是具体的实现方法并不是数据结构的本身。</p><p><strong>R1-4</strong> 斐波那契数列Fn的定义为：F0=0, F1=1, Fn=Fn−1+Fn−2, N=2, 3, …用递归函数计算Fn的空间复杂度是<em>O</em>(N)。 <strong><font color=red>T</font></strong></p><p><strong>【解】</strong> 树的高度是n，F(n)只要没到出口 n&lt;2 就会一直在当前函数栈里开辟新空间。[补充]递归函数求Fibonacci数列的时间复杂度为**<font color=red> 2^n </font>**</p><p><strong>R1-9</strong> <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wq3stone/picgo//img/202205072004963.png" alt="image-20220507200404924"></p><p>【解】 不会</p><p><strong>R2-5</strong> 下列代码的时间复杂度是**<font color=red> O(N^3) </font>**</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> ( A &gt; B )</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> ( i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;N; i++ )</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> ( j=N*N; j&gt;i; j-- )</span><br><span class="line">            A += B;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> ( i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;N*<span class="number">2</span>; i++ )</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> ( j=N*<span class="number">2</span>; j&gt;i; j-- )</span><br><span class="line">            A += B;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>R2-10</strong> 若栈采用顺序存储方式存储，现两栈共享空间<code>V[m]</code>：<code>top[i]</code>代表第<code>i</code>（<code>i</code>=1或2）个栈的栈顶；栈1的底在<code>V[0]</code>，栈2的底在<code>V[m-1]</code>，则栈满的条件是：**<font color=red>top[1]+1==top[2]</font>**</p><p><strong>R2-15</strong> 给定程序时间复杂度的递推公式：<em>T</em>(1)=1，<em>T</em>(<em>N</em>)=2<em>T</em>(<em>N</em>/2)+<em>N</em>。则对该程序时间复杂度最接近的描述是：**<font color=red>O(NlogN)</font>**</p><p><strong>【解】</strong> 解析：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">T(2N) = 2T(N) + 2N</span><br><span class="line">T(2N)/(2N) = T(N)/N + 1</span><br><span class="line">令C(N) = T(N)/N</span><br><span class="line">C(2N) - C(N) = 1</span><br><span class="line">令2N = 2^k</span><br><span class="line">C(2^k) - C(2^(k-1)) = 1</span><br><span class="line">C(2^(k-1))  - C(2^(k-2))  = 1</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">C(2) - C(1) = 1</span><br><span class="line">累加上式得</span><br><span class="line">C(2^k) = k + C(1)</span><br><span class="line">令 n = 2^k</span><br><span class="line">k = log2(n)</span><br><span class="line">T(n)/n = log2(n) + C(1)</span><br><span class="line">T(n) =  nlog2(n) + nC(1)</span><br><span class="line">所以时间复杂度为O(NlogN)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>R2-17</strong> 程序P1和P2时间复杂度的递推公式：</p><p>P1: <em>T</em> (1) = 1, <em>T</em>(<em>N</em>) = <em>T</em> ( <em>N</em> / 2) + 1;</p><p>P2: <em>T</em> (1) = 1, <em>T</em>(<em>N</em>) = 2<em>T</em> ( <em>N</em> / 2) + 1;</p><p>则下列关于两程序时间复杂度的结论中最准确的是：**<font color=red>P1为O(logN)，P2为O(N)</font>**</p>]]></content>
      
      
